        "date": "2026-07-13T03:52:26Z",
        "message": "Merge pull request #3182 from thedotmack/cloud-sync-native\n\nfeat(sync): worker-native cloud sync — the database is the queue",
        "url": "https://github.com/thedotmack/claude-mem/commit/7a9c9b0618b392fc67c005c784c745a68c218761"
